title: Formula1 2013 Round10 Hungary Race TSNHD x264 English
description:
Release Information:  
Video:             x264, avc-1, Level 4.1

Race coverage of the HungarianGrand Prix with BBC commentary. Starts from 5 minutes before the race start and ends after the podium interviews. For a brief moment they witched to the natural sounds feed because the BBC one had some on and off picture issues.
There are ads in as there are side by side. Please do not complain about that in the comments as I have already told you
